'''Skype''' is a proprietary application owned by Microsoft for instant messaging, VoIP calls, and video conversations.

== Installation ==

=== USE flags ===

{{USEflag|package=net-im/skype}}

=== Emerge ===

Install {{Package|net-im/skype}}:

{{Emerge|net-im/skype}}

By default, Gentoo installations do not include acceptance of Skype's license, so users wanting to install will need to add the following to {{Path|/etc/portage/package.license}}:

{{FileBox|filename=/etc/portage/package.license|title=Necessary license acceptance for Skype|1=
net-im/skype skype-4.0.0.7-copyright
}}

